The appliance can be controlled via command line tools and the web
service API.  The command line tools are named vp-* and can be run
with --help. The main features are starting clusters, transfering
data, and running pipelines. Visit clovr.org for more documentation

#Authentication
vp-add-credential
vp-describe-credentials  

#Cluster tools
vp-start-cluster         
vp-describe-cluster      
vp-terminate-cluster

#Pipeline tools
vp-run-pipeline          
vp-describe-pipeline     
vp-add-instances         

#Datasets
vp-add-dataset           
vp-download-dataset      
vp-transfer-dataset
vp-describe-dataset      

#Metrics
vp-run-metrics           

#System startup and shutdown scripts
vp-start-platform
vp-stop-platform
vp-start-node            
vp-stop-node

